Where do I get my Lego?
- Bricklink.com, and the Lego store
How do I make my videos?
- To edit, I use Final Cut Pro X. To film, I use a Canon EOS R8 and my iPhone. To record my voice, I use a RODE VideoMic Go.
Do I have instructions for my Lego builds?
- No
What do I do with my Lego builds after a video is finished?
- I have to take them apart to use for the next video

snippet.title: Hathras stampede: An avoidable tragedy? | Former IPS Vikram Singh | Faye D'Souza
snippet.description:
121 people died, and several others were injured, in a stampede during a satsang hosted by a local preacher Narayan Sakar Vishwa Hari aka ‘Bhole Baba’ in Uttar Pradesh’s Hathras on Tuesday. Preliminary investigation reveals several glaring lapses in how the event was conducted. Faye speaks to former UP top cop Vikram Singh about what went wrong.

snippet.title: The Bombay Dream by Mukesh Chhabra With Farah Khan/ S01 EP 01
snippet.description:
Director, Choreographer, Producer - Farah Khan wears many hats!
Right from her first directorial debut 'Main Hoon Na', she is known for her stellar casting, having successfully cast many multi-starrer movies. With an eye for talent, she sits down with director Mukesh Chhabra to spill the beans in our all new show 'The Bombay Dream' presented by LG QNED. Getting rejected by many known talents for now popular characters to actors lying to her about their talents for the role, to her relationship with Shahrukh Khan - Farah reveals it all!

snippet.title: Kabir Khan with Mukesh Chhabra /  The Bombay Dream S01   EP04 #bollywood #castingdirector #casting
snippet.description:
#KatrinaKaif #ShahrukhKhan #SalmanKhan
Kabir Khan - the vision behind Bajrangi Bhaijaan, 83, Ek Tha Tiger and New York, brings to you secrets and stories from his sets, his casting choices and so much more in the latest episode of The Bombay Dream with Mukesh Chhabra, presented by LG OLED!
He speaks about casting Salman Khan & Katrina Kaif after their breakup for Ek Tha Tiger, him studying for his exams from Shahrukh Khan's notes to revealing what is takes to be a Kabir Khan's actor - he reveals all!

Mukesh Chhabra is the driving force behind streamlining the casting process in the Hindi Film Industry. After training for 2 years to understand the craft of acting from Shri Ram Centre, he completed 9 years acting and teaching with the ‘Theatre in Education’ Company (TIE) affiliated with the National School of Drama in India. Mukesh Chhabra Casting Company, founded in 2008, has grown to become the leading casting company in India. With an eye for talent, Mukesh Chhabra has discovered faces like Rajkummar Rao, Sushant Singh Rajput, Mrunal Thakur, Pratik Gandhi, Sanya Malhotra and Fatima Sana Shaikh. MCCC believes in nurturing new talents to carve a niche in the big bustling world of Hindi Cinema. Some of his notable works include Gangs of Wasseypur {2012,} Highway
2014  Bajrangi Bhaijan (2015), Bombay Velvet (2015), Dangal (2016), Dil Bechara (2020), Scam 1992 (2020), Laal Singh Chaddha (2022), Commando (2023), Jawan (2023), Dunki (2023), Chamak (2023) and Kafas (2023).12th Fail [2023], Amar Singh Chamkila, [2024],

snippet.title: Vicky Kaushal Interview with Anupama Chopra | Bad Newz | Film Companion
snippet.description:
In this conversation with Anupama Chopra, Vicky Kaushal talks about all things Tauba Tauba, his urge to be a part of such an extravagant dance number, and the love he’s received for the same, especially from his wife Katrina Kaif. He delves into his relationship with Anand Tiwari, the director of Bad Newz, and how a healthy director-actor relationship translates into art being delivered better. He talks about his next - Chaava, the challenges he faced while preparing himself to play Chhatrapati Sambhaji Maharaj, and how he plans on moving into and past his 10th year, at the movies. 

#VickyKaushal #BadNewz #TaubaTauba

Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.title: Child’s happiness is equal to mother’s wellness - Samyuktha about her fitness journey | Smart Talks
snippet.description:
“Fitness played a huge role”- Actress Samyuktha on her Fitness Journey | Smart Talks | Smart Ovaries

Smart Talks with Smart Ovaries is a Podcast series by Dr.Sharanya.T, Gynaecologist. She interacts with health care industry Experts and other well known fitness enthusiasts, Influencers on their journey, Struggles faced and the motivation that directed them towards their successful journey.

For all the doubts that we wanted to ask, she asked the field experts on our behalf and got the  smart answers..!! 

“Smart Talks” is all set to reach you every week from now on.

Stay Tuned!

Behind the Lens: Vishal, Vishvesh and Team Dimensions

snippet.title: Ambani Wedding | A Star Studded Shubh Ashirwad Ceremony For Anant-Radhika | Bollywood | N18V
snippet.description:
After months of pre-wedding festivities, Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant tied the knot on Friday in Mumbai. The wedding was a grand affair that was attended by the likes of Amitabh Bachchan, Rajinikanth, John Cena, Kim Kardashian, Shah Rukh Khan, Madhuri Dixit, Salman Khan, Priyanka Chopra, Katrina Kaif, Vicky Kaushal, Alia Bhatt, Ranbir Kapoor, Deepika Padukone, Ranveer Singh, Aishwarya Rai, Rekha, among many others. The wedding saw performances by King, Rema, Luis Fonsi.

Photos and videos from the wedding were everywhere on social media on Friday night. On Saturday, the family is hosting an ‘Aashirvaad’ ceremony, which will also be graced by celebrities. This will be followed by a grand reception on Sunday.

snippet.title: Nana Patekar ने Vidhu Vinod, Sanjay Bhansali से लड़ाई, Tiranga, Raj Kumar, Tanushree पर सब बतायाGITN
snippet.description:
Register here to be part of GITN Shoot- https://rb.gy/nbu7hi
Naam Foundation website- https://naammh.org/

Veteran actor Nana Patekar joins the 100th episode of Guest in the Newsroom for a captivating conversation. He reminisces about his illustrious career, sharing anecdotes from his iconic films like Tiranga, Wajood, Prahaar, and Welcome. Nana also openly addresses the Me Too allegations made against him by actress Tanushree Dutta. He delves into his early struggles in the industry and his days in theater. Nana fondly recalls working with Rajkumar in Tiranga and shares several interesting stories from his career. He narrates amusing incidents from his roles in films like Wajood, Prahaar, Tiranga, and Salaam Bombay. Additionally, Nana discusses the many memes featuring him that have gone viral. Don't miss this special interview with Nana Patekar, hosted by Saurabh Dwivedi.

Key Points:

Nana Patekar's remarkable film career
Early struggles and theater days
Working with Rajkumar in Tiranga

Veteran actor Nana Patekar joins the 100th episode of Guest in the Newsroom for a captivating conversation. He reminisces about his illustrious career, sharing anecdotes from his iconic films like Tiranga, Wajood, Prahaar, and Welcome. Nana also openly addresses the Me Too allegations made against him by actress Tanushree Dutta. He delves into his early struggles in the industry and his days in theater. Nana fondly recalls working with Rajkumar in Tiranga and shares several interesting stories from his career. He narrates amusing incidents from his roles in films like Wajood, Prahaar, Tiranga, and Salaam Bombay. Additionally, Nana discusses the many memes featuring him that have gone viral. Don't miss this special interview with Nana Patekar, hosted by Saurabh Dwivedi.

Key Points:

Nana Patekar's remarkable film career
Early struggles and theater days
Working with Rajkumar in Tiranga
Anecdotes from films like Wajood, Prahaar, Tiranga, and Salaam Bombay
Viral memes featuring Nana Patekar

snippet.description:
#LTChunav #ChunavYatra #LallantopChunav

शुरू हो चुकी है लल्लनटॉप की चुनाव यात्रा. बताइए क्या है आपकी लोकसभा सीट का नाम और कवरेज की वजह? कौन से फैक्टर आपकी सीट को बनाते हैं ख़ास. सब्जेक्ट में 'मेरी सीट कवर करो' लिखकर भेज दीजिए मेल Chunav@Lallantop.com या लिंक पर क्लिक करें.
Link: https://forms.gle/uaRg378VkP9Jb88T8

Guest House Scandal 1995. An incident which changed the political landscape of the most populous state of the India, Uttar Pradesh. What exactly happened that day? In the latest episode of Kitabwala, Lallantop’s premium book show, we interviewed, former DGP of Uttar Pradesh, who also was the SSP of Lucknow when Guest House Scandal happened on 2nd June 1995. Join in to watch the full conversation. Along with this, various other issues of prominence importance of 90's were also discussed, like the impact of Khalistan movement in Lakhimpur Khiri and the encounter of Mahender Fauji which led to the tussle in SP-BSP government.

#LallantopBaithki #Baithki Episode 13.


The Lallantop brings to you a brand-new chat show - Baithki. In this show, people from different fields will come face to face with you. In this episode of Baithki, our guest is Amitabh Yash.


Amitabh Yash is an IPS officer who is currently serving as the Additional Director General of Police (ADG) of the Special Task Force (STF) in Uttar Pradesh. The Special Task Force is a specialized unit of the Uttar Pradesh Police that is responsible for handling high-profile and complex cases, such as organized crime, terrorism, and cybercrime. As the ADG of the STF, Amitabh Yash is responsible for overseeing the operations of the unit and ensuring that it achieves its objectives in maintaining law and order in the state. Amitabh Yash has a distinguished career in the police force, having served in various positions of responsibility in the Uttar Pradesh Police. He has been involved in several high-profile cases and has received several accolades for his contribution to the maintenance of law and order in the state. He is known for his strict discipline and no-nonsense approach, and is respected by his peers and subordinates alike.

As the ADG of the STF, Amitabh Yash is responsible for overseeing the operations of the unit and ensuring that it achieves its objectives in maintaining law and order in the state. Amitabh Yash has a distinguished career in the police force, having served in various positions of responsibility in the Uttar Pradesh Police. He has been involved in several high-profile cases and has received several accolades for his contribution to the maintenance of law and order in the state. He is known for his strict discipline and no-nonsense approach, and is respected by his peers and subordinates alike.

snippet.title: Why Bhojpuri Films Are LIKE THIS?
snippet.description:
Check out Odoo: https://www.odoo.com/r/I2P

****** 
What comes to mind when you think of Bhojpuri movies? Probably low-quality production, exaggerated characters, and explicit content. But Bhojpuri films weren't always like this. They once featured mature themes and had legends like Mohammad Rafi and Lata Mangeshkar singing their songs. So, what happened to give Bhojpuri cinema such a negative reputation today? Join me on a fascinating journey through the rise and fall of the Bhojpuri film industry, uncovering the reasons behind its decline and how it contributed to the stereotyping of Bihari people.

******

In the glorious era of saas-bahu serials, where every dramatic twist was more mind-boggling than the last, the nation witnessed a phenomenon – Mihir's death in 'Kyun ki saas bhi kabhi bahu thi.' As women gathered to protest his demise, one might wonder if the nation collectively needed a dose of reality. Fast forward to the present, where Indian TV serials are struggling to retain their charm, and even the once-mighty 'Anupama' faces a viewership decline. So, what really went wrong? Why aren't Indian TV serials able to appeal to the audiences anymore? That's what we shall try to find in this video.

******

Indian Film Industry means glamour but are you aware of its not-so-glamourous side? Have you ever wondered why so many movies fail despite big stars? Grand Indian weddings are vibrant, elaborate affairs filled with rich traditions and celebrations. These multi-day events are marked by colorful decorations, intricate rituals, and joyous music and dance. Families come together to celebrate with lavish feasts, elaborate ceremonies like the Sangeet, Mehendi, and Baraat. Bridal attire is often adorned with exquisite jewelry and traditional garments. Each wedding showcases a blend of cultural heritage and modern elements, creating a unique experience for every couple. With opulent venues and detailed planning, grand Indian weddings are truly a spectacle of love, family, and festivity.

snippet.description:
Kahani Kursi Ki : शहीद कैप्टन अंशुमान सिंह की पत्नी पर स्मृति ने क्यों किया सास- ससुर के साथ अन्याय?
दिल्ली पुलिस की ‘इंटेलिजेंस फ्यूजन एंड स्ट्रैटेजिक ऑपरेशन’ (IFSO) सेल ने कीर्ति चक्र से सम्मानित (मरणोपरांत) कैप्टन अंशुमान सिंह की पत्नी स्मृति सिंह पर ‘X’ पर कथित रूप से अभद्र टिप्पणी करने को लेकर FIR दर्ज की है। राष्ट्रीय महिला आयोग (NCW) ने सोमवार को स्वत: संज्ञान लेते हुए इस मामले में दिल्ली पुलिस के समक्ष शिकायत दर्ज कराई थी।

दिल्ली पुलिस की ‘इंटेलिजेंस फ्यूजन एंड स्ट्रैटेजिक ऑपरेशन’ (IFSO) सेल ने कीर्ति चक्र से सम्मानित (मरणोपरांत) कैप्टन अंशुमान सिंह की पत्नी स्मृति सिंह पर ‘X’ पर कथित रूप से अभद्र टिप्पणी करने को लेकर FIR दर्ज की है। राष्ट्रीय महिला आयोग (NCW) ने सोमवार को स्वत: संज्ञान लेते हुए इस मामले में दिल्ली पुलिस के समक्ष शिकायत दर्ज कराई थी।

snippet.title: Haqeeqat Kya Hai: मोदी विरोधी का एक ही काम..बोलो संविधान..संविधान | PM Modi | Rahul Gandhi | BJP
snippet.description:
नरेंद्र मोदी अब आक्रमण करेंगे..ईंट का जवाब पत्थर से दिया जाएगा। अब चुपचाप हमला नहीं सहा जाएगा। अगर विरोधी..संविधान..संविधान करेंगे..संविधान की कॉपी पॉकेट में लेकर घूमेंगे..तो उन्हें इमरजेंसी वाला चैप्टर याद दिलाया जाएगा। अगर मोदी के विरोधी संविधान बचाओ का नारा लगाएंगे..तो मोदी की पार्टी संविधान हत्या दिवस ज़ोर शोर से मनाएगी। 2024 के चुनावी नतीजों का जब बीजेपी ने मंथन किया..तो एक बात समझ में आई...और वो ये..कि विरोधियों ने फेक नैरेटिव का जाल ऐसे बुना...कि वोटर कन्फ्यूज हो गया..चकमे में आ गया। और ये फेक नैरेटिव चला ही जा रहा है। उप-चुनाव के रिज़ल्ट भी क्या उसी फेक नैरेटिव का नतीजा हैं? या फिर बिल्कुल नई बात वोटर तक चल रही है? क्या सरकार के खिलाफ कोई नया माहौल खड़ा हो गया है?

snippet.title: Uparwala Dekh Raha Hai Full Episode: नेता प्रतिपक्ष पर देखिए आजतक का ये खास शो | Rahul Gandhi | BJP
snippet.description:
कांग्रेस प्रवक्ता सुप्रिया श्रीनेत ने कहा है कि पॉपुलैरिटी गेन में ना राहुल गांधी हैं ना PM मोदी हैं, देश डिमांड कर रहा है कि आज की राजनीति मुद्दों पर की जाए, पीएम मोदी 2 घंटा 14 मिनट अगर बोल रहे हैं और सदन मणिपुर को न्याय दो के नारों से गूंज रहा है और 15 महीने बाद प्रधानमंत्री मणिपुर नहीं जा रहे हैं और राहुल गांधी तीसरी बार जाए रहे हैं तो ये स्टार्क तुलना होने आप में ही हो जाती है. राजनीतिक विश्लेषक आशुतोष ने कहा है कि मैंने जितना वेस्ट मिनिस्टर मॉडल पढ़ा उसमें स्पीकर को चेयरमैन को शायद सबसे कम बोलना चाहिए लेकिन दुर्भाग्य है कि सबसे ज्यादा वार्तालाप चेयर से होता है, इसका मतलब कि आप संसद को संभाल नहीं पा रहे हैं या विपक्ष आपका सम्मान नहीं कर पा रहा है या सत्तपक्ष और विपक्ष के बीच की केमिस्ट्री आप मैनेज नहीं कर पा रहे हैं, मुझे लगता है कि पिछले दस साल में राहुल गांधी के साथ-सा संथसद का चरित्र भी बदला है.

snippet.title: बद्रीनाथ में बीजेपी हारी, बंगाल में भी हार | INDIA sweeps bypolls
snippet.description:
बद्रीनाथ में भी बीजेपी हार गई है। विधानसभा का उपचुनाव था लेकिन लोकसभा चुनाव में अयोध्या हारने के बाद बदरीनाथ में बीजेपी हार जाएगी इस खबर की चर्चा होनी ही थी। इस जीत के साथ ही लखपत सिंह बुटोला अयोध्या के सांसद अवधेश प्रसाद की तरह लोकप्रिय हो गए हैं। जिन 13 सीटों पर उपचुनाव हुए हैं, उनमें से दस पर INDIA गठबंधन जीत गया है। लोकसभा चुनाव में विपक्ष के प्रदर्शन के बाद यह नतीजे बीजेपी के लिए चिंताजनक हैं। बंगाल में टीएमसी चारों सीटों पर जीत गई है, उस इलाक़े में भी जो बीजेपी का गढ़ माना जाता है।

snippet.title: A ‘jai jawan, jai kisan’ trap awaits Modi. In a 5-year Test match with revived Opposition
snippet.description:
The BJP and partners won a points victory as if in a boxing match. The victory wasn’t narrow. But it was no quick knockout like the last two. Their rivals were able to land some punches, are still in the ring, on their feet, and fighting. Think of the 2024 verdict as a qualifier in which the Opposition earned the right to challenge the title holder in a kind of Test championship final.

snippet.title: Should India Recognise Tibet As Occupied, Call China's Bluff?
snippet.description:
Resolve Tibet Law

"We welcome U.S. President Joe Biden signing the bill to enact the 'Resolve Tibet' Act into law." Dorjee Tseten, Member of the Tibetan Parliament in exile tells StratNews Global. As a matter of fact, on July 13, 2024, in a statement, the President of the United States (POTUS) signed into "law S. 138, the “Promoting a Resolution to the Tibet-China Dispute Act” (the “Act”)." Additionally, he stated, "I share the Congress’ bipartisan commitment to advancing the human rights of Tibetans". As well as "supporting efforts to preserve their distinct linguistic, cultural, and religious heritage". At the same time the statement said, "My Administration will continue to call on the People’s Republic of China to resume direct dialogue, without preconditions, with the Dalai Lama, or his representatives, to seek a settlement that resolves differences and leads to a negotiated agreement on Tibet."

Tibet & China's Expansionism

Dr. Tenzin Dorjee (TenDor), a strategist at the Tibet Action Institute and Dorjee Tseten speak to StratNews Global Associate Editor Amitabh P. Revi in this comprehensive conversation. At any rate, after Biden signed the act into law, Dorjee said, "This explicitly rejects as inaccurate China’s false claims that Tibet has been part of China since ancient times. The strong language of the bill demonstrates the U.S.' renewed commitment to advocating for the Tibetan people’s right of self-determination". Furthermore, he added, "This is in accordance with international law. By designating Tibet as an unresolved conflict, this bill, which is now law, has major implications for India". " Above all, "not least because it bolsters India’s position against China's expansionist policies in the Himalayan region," Dorjee added.

At the same time, TenDor is emphatic in saying, "It is important that recognizing Tibet as an occupied country and Tibetans having a right to self-determination is, by international law, our right as a collective right.  It is very important for India, especially with China's expansionist policy".

Dorjee reveals that "Dharamsala has been targeted by the Chinese government, from the very beginning. It's not a new thing. And we try to learn. We try to protect ourselves both digitally and physically."

Reacting to the 'Resolve Tibet' law, Tibetologist Claude Arpi told StratNews Global, "Unfortunately there is a rider. The One-China Policy is reiterated in the same communique: “The Act does not change longstanding bipartisan United States policy to recognize the Tibet Autonomous Region and other Tibetan areas of China as part of the People’s Republic of China.” In these circumstances, it is difficult to see how the new law will concretely help the Dalai Lama and his countrymen in the near future. In view of the present authoritarian regime in Beijing (and the deep antagonism between the U.S. and China), how Washington can help “resolve differences and lead to a negotiated agreement on Tibet”, is not clear.

TenDor and Dorjee also discuss:

-Their personal lives and connections with India.
-The 'Resolve Tibet' Law in the U.S.
-The U.S. appeasement under Nixon-Kissinger.
-Current U.S.-China confrontation.
-Chinese attempts to erase Tibet.
-India as a bulwark in support of Tibetans.
-Chinese Communist Party (CCP) attempts at infiltration and influence.
-A need for a coordinated front against the CCP.
-The Dalai Lama and his succession.
-and the need for India's foreign policy to put China on the backfoot.

#Tibet #China #India #DalaiLama #XiJinping
